  "2026-04-06T17:08:53.092Z",codex-agent,"Progress: shipped new pm update-many command with filter selectors, deterministic dry-run item diff preview, checkpoint file creation, apply execution summaries, and --rollback restore workflow. Rollback uses captured target updated_at values per item to replay precise restores and emits per-item restored or failed rows."
